article.description: — Ikenna Ndugba posted 17 points as Elon defeated William & Mary 73-54 on Monday night.
article.headline: Ndugba scores 17 to lead Elon over William & Mary 73-54
article.linkText: Ndugba scores 17 to lead Elon over William & Mary 73-54
article.story: ELON, N.C. -- — Ikenna Ndugba posted 17 points as Elon defeated William & Mary 73-54 on Monday night. Darius Burford had 13 points and six rebounds for Elon (6-8, 3-7 Colonial Athletic Association). Chuck Hannah added 10 points. The Phoenix forced a season-high 21 turnovers. Luke Loewe had 15 points for the Tribe (6-9, 4-6). Yuri Covington added 13 points and Quinn Blair had 12. The Phoenix improve to 2-0 against the Tribe on the season. Elon defeated William & Mary 75-54 last Saturday. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
